<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥaẘlaka naḥ̊nu naj̊tamiʿ̊
 yā rabãnā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 nadẖ̊kuru ḥubãka ạlãdẖī
 badā ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V2]
 2- yā lahu ḥubaⁿ̃ạ fāyỉḍaⁿạ
 min̊ qal̊bika yaj̊rī
 ʿanãạ ḥusib̊ta mudẖ̊nibaⁿạ
 maʿ̊ ạảnãka ạl̊barī

[V3]
 3- wahakadẖā lạảj̊linā
 qad̊ mutã biạkẖ̊tīār̊
 naʿ̊m̊! waqad̊ ạảẘṣaẙtanā
 ạản̊ naṣ̊naʿa ạltãdẖ̊kār̊

[V4]
 4- yadẖ̊kuru ḥubãka ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 qal̊bī wāảf̊kārī
 ạản̊ta ạlãdẖī qul̊ta ạṣ̊naʿūạ
 hadẖā litadẖ̊kārī

[V5]
 5- wāản̊ta ṣāḥibu ạl̊ʿasẖā
 wālsãyĩdu lanā
 min̊ yadika nan̊taẓiru
 ạltãẘzīʿa kulũnā

[V6]
 6- nadẖ̊kuru daẘmaⁿạ ḥubãka
 naf̊raḥu ạảẙḍaⁿạ fīk̊
 wanukẖ̊biru bimaẘtika
 hunā ại̹lay̱ majīk̊</lyrics>
<title>ḥwlk nḥn njtmʿ</title>
<copyright>1977</copyright>
</song>